    <item>
        <title>easyCal 0.3.0</title>
        <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
        <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
        <pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:00:12 +0200</pubDate>
        <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h2>easyCal 0.3.0</h2>
<ul>
<li>Clickable URLs on reminders — links attached via URL field or detected in notes now show an interactive icon</li>
<li>GitHub icon for GitHub links — reminders linking to GitHub issues/projects display a distinct icon for quick recognition</li>
<li>"Open on GitHub" / "Open Link" context menu for reminders with URLs in both Reminders panel and Agenda view</li>
</ul>
        ]]></description>
